statements: SELECT * FROM website_traffic;
SELECT user_id, page_url FROM website_traffic WHERE interaction_type = 'click';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM website_traffic;
SELECT MAX(timestamp) FROM website_traffic WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT AVG(user_id) AS average_user_id FROM website_traffic;
SELECT user_id, page_url FROM website_traffic WHERE interaction_type='click' ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE interaction_type='scroll' AND user_id = 123 ORDER BY timestamp ASC
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_traffic GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY visit_count DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT timestamp, page_url FROM website_traffic WHERE interaction_type='hover' AND timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY timestamp
SELECT user_id, MIN(timestamp) AS first_interaction_time FROM website_traffic GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY first_interaction_time ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM website_traffic;
SELECT website_id, page_id, user_id, timestamp, activity FROM website_traffic WHERE website_id = 1;
SELECT user_id, interaction_id, interaction_type FROM user_interactions ORDER BY interaction_timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, interaction_id, interaction_type, interaction_timestamp FROM user_interactions WHERE user_id = 100;
SELECT website_id, COUNT(page_id) AS total_page_views FROM website_traffic GROUP BY website_id;
SELECT website_id, page_id, user_id, timestamp, activity FROM website_traffic WHERE user_id = 100 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT user_id, interaction_id, interaction_type, interaction_timestamp FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_type = 'click' AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM interaction_timestamp) = 9 ORDER BY interaction_timestamp ASC;
SELECT website_id, COUNT(DISTINCT user_id) AS unique_users FROM website_traffic GROUP BY website_id HAVING unique_users > 100 ORDER BY unique_users DESC;
SELECT website_id, page_id, user_id, timestamp, activity FROM website_traffic WHERE activity LIKE '%login%' OR activity LIKE '%signup%' ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT website_id, COUNT(*) AS total_interactions FROM website_traffic GROUP BY website_id ORDER BY total_interactions DESC;

SELECT user_id, COUNT(view_id) FROM page_views GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(view_id) > 10;
SELECT product_name, price FROM products WHERE category = 'Electronics' ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT * FROM users;
SELECT user_name, email FROM users WHERE registration_date > '2021-01-01';
SELECT user_name, email FROM users ORDER BY user_name ASC;
SELECT user_name, email, category FROM users JOIN products ON users.user_id = products.product_id;
SELECT user_name, email, category, price FROM users JOIN products ON users.user_id = products.product_id WHERE price > 50.00 ORDER BY price DESC;

SELECT * FROM website_users;

SELECT * FROM website_pages ORDER BY page_name DESC;

SELECT u.username, p.page_name, t.traffic_time FROM website_users u JOIN website_traffic t ON u.user_id = t.user_id JOIN website_pages p ON t.page_id = p.page_id ORDER BY t.traffic_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_visits;
